## Conclusion

It's hard to say too much about the third batch of hymns because not too many wards have sung those hymns so far. We're starting to see which are more popular than others and when they're sung during the meeting. What is clear though is the relatively cold reception these hymns have gotten. After a month, still only a small proportion of wards have sung from this third batch. But, the past two weeks have shown some signs of greater use. As we approach Easter, we might see more and more wards singing these new hymns.
